Cart module for Kohana 2.3.4

CONFIGURATION (config/wcart.php)
$config['model_name'] = 'Product_Model'; // the name of you product model
$config['prod_id'] = 'id'; // the ID column of the product table
$config['name'] = 'name'; // the column where is stored the name of the product
$config['price'] = 'price'; // the column where is stored the name of the product


USE:
$this->cart = new Wcart(); // create a new instance
$this->cart->load_session(); // load the session: NEEDED


